data.description: Get your family and friends ready for your backyard pool party. Lots of upgrades in home and also has two back covered patios.  This spacious home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths on almost a 1/2 acre lot.  Home offers several upgrades which includes a beautiful remodeled kitchen brand new dishwasher, remodeled guest bathroom, new central A/C, furnace, and new electrical box changed from 120 amps to 220 amps. Home located on a dead-end street that is very quiet. Please verify rooms sizes.
